milestones.description: Athar Ali Khan has become the top scorer for BAN in ODIs with 190 runs, going past Minhajul Abedin's 116
Minhajul Abedin has become the top wicket-taker for BAN in ODIs with 5 wickets, going past Gholam Nousher's 4
Athar Ali Khan's 78 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BAN), surpassing Faruque Ahmed's 57
Ranatunga and de Silva's 139-run partnership is SL's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 110 between Roy Dias and Ranatunga
Minhajul Abedin and Athar Ali Khan's 50-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 43 between Shaheedur Rahman and Minhajul Abedin
This is the highest match aggregate (427) involving teams Sri Lanka & Bangladesh in ODIs
Gholam Nousher has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for BAN, going past Minhajul Abedin
